## 17. Fluxo resumido

```
ENTRADA (recebida)
  Neonize MessageEv
    → WhatsAppManager.on_message (dedup + token check)
      → MessageHandler.handle_incoming_message
          → WhatsAppContact (get_or_create)
          → Conversation (get_or_create)
          → Message (create)
          → Sentimento inline (Gemini ou keywords)
          → IA response (opcional)

SAÍDA (enviada)
  views.send_message (POST)
    → MessageHandler.create_outgoing_message
    → NeonizeClient.send_text (asyncio.run)
    → Message.status = 'sent'

CHATPRO (webhook externo → CRM)
  POST /api/webhooks/chatpro/<token>/
    → Valida token → Extrai phone/body
    → Lead (get_or_create por phone_normalized)
    → LeadOpportunity (Kanban)
    → LeadNote + LeadActivity
```

